{"tid":640993,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[火牛]求連登高手解答火牛問題","createTime":"2018-04-24T16:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T18:33:48.000Z","uid":35281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7fb4fbffafc15f381a836f1f300c08c9d9c4b59","tid":640993,"uid":35281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"早幾日notebook火牛燒咗<br />\n之後去旺角買咗個火牛用住先<br />\n但係充緊電個陣用耳機會聽到類似電波嘅聲<br />\n<br />\n以下係舊火牛同新火牛嘅數值<br />\n舊:<br />\ninput: 100-240V~50-60Hz 2.0A<br />\noutput: 19.5V =6.15A<br />\n新:<br />\ninput: 100-240V~2.2A 50-60Hz<br />\noutput: 19.5V =6.15A<br />\n新同舊都係寫住120W<br />\n(個=號係上面一橫下面三點)<br />\n<br />\n除咗耳機電波聲之外都冇咩問題<br />\n想問下咁多位連登巴打個問題係咪個新火牛個input個到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋keep住用會唔會有問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申冇讀過phy 唔想爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6fa36f5df685e0088a5c7c37e7b4abb1505f90","tid":640993,"uid":35281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0cee52ab2cf497c5a5940e64f33adfa7611e11","tid":640993,"uid":35281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94ae7e4b5e83bbe9e36a7ee71ee00dc6f60fdf6","tid":640993,"uid":139538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"充電時用手掂，火牛會唔會辣手<br />\n<br />\n乜牌子火牛，拎去換其他牌子"},{"pid":"d683cfaff1ee58d709a8d06bd575cf47b5b4f843","tid":640993,"uid":35281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0